                "description": "Simple send API. Preferred body: `{ to, text }`. Backward compatible aliases: `toPhone`, `message`.\n\n`to` is normalized to digits.\n\n**Success:** `ok=true` with `id`, `toPhone`, `status`, `metaMessageId`.\n**Failure:** `502` with Meta reason + saved `messageLog`."
